{"tid":1725022,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"與其話大學比鬼混入 不如話連登比鬼混入","createTime":"2019-11-15T15:33:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T15:37:58.000Z","uid":155133,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6ac1c34b458de04c59dc1fc2e89a80457922e2f6","tid":1725022,"uid":155133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:33:40.000Z","msg":"好耐冇睇連登<br />\n一入黎成版都係講鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你老母 講左好撚多次<br />\n入得去守個個都係手足兄弟<br />\n搵條命搏<br />\n宜家守橋都比人話係鬼 收皮啦<br />\n<br />\n就算真係理大捉鬼<br />\n中大爆玻璃咁又點<br />\n手足都係人<br />\n唔會每樣野都決定得啱<br />\n<br />\n作為一個經常係前線既人<br />\n爭執係會有<br />\n但一定唔會割蓆<br />\n嘈完都係各有各做<br />\n唔會話手足係鬼<br />\n<br />\n反而連登係咁吹風<br />\n又話呢度鬼個度鬼<br />\n係咁叫人走<br />\n一係就話唔係自己人<br />\n搞到我有啲剩係睇連登既同事又信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登除左睇新聞真係咩都唔好睇<br />\n尤其係吹風post <br />\n食屎啦五毛狗"},{"pid":"b742c9f4bd68dd236acf119bf059a8555cc9b222","tid":1725022,"uid":321977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:34:27.000Z","msg":"借個位，幫手多謝下人發聲，人地係支國咁多讀者都出聲，幫推！<br />\n<br />\n[突發]台灣作家九把刀因分享撐香港歌曲而被五毛攻擊！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1724951\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1724951</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"398fefc26e85d82e26230923a0716722e609a40e","tid":1725022,"uid":155133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:34:51.000Z","msg":"食屎啦五毛狗"},{"pid":"cbd4cabe2068182e698e5b8b6a29c3cecba77d67","tid":1725022,"uid":155133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:35:04.000Z","msg":"食屎啦五毛狗"},{"pid":"4110d7f49cc22027d5d4b9899140859cd87b05f4","tid":1725022,"uid":155133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:35:15.000Z","msg":"食屎啦五毛狗"},